doc.after: The RC 135V W is the USAF s standard airborne SIGINT platform Its sensor suite allows the mission crew to detect identify and geolocate signals throughout the electromagnetic spectrum The mission crew can then forward gathered information in a variety of formats to a wide range of consumers via Rivet Joint s extensive communications suite The crew consists of the cockpit crew electronic warfare officers intelligence operators and airborne systems maintenance personnel All Rivet Joint airframe and mission systems modifications are performed by L 3 Communications in Greenville Texas under the oversight of the Air Force Materiel Command 4
